This paper deals with developing a student performance prediction model using data mining techniques. The paper uses machine learning algorithms such as SVM, RF, KNN, and MLP to train the model. The paper also uses state-of-the-art partitioning schemes and Label Powerset transformation method to improve the performance of the prediction model. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) followed by cs.CE (Computational Engineering), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
